title: Turret Red White Green Stripe Glass Ornament—Large
description:
The ornaments are handmade on a torch using the flameworking technique, in which a flame is used to melt and shape glass tubing and colored glass rods by blowing and shaping with tools and hand movements into desired shapes. Each unique piece is handmade in Pittsburgh PA.

Mouth Blown Glass Turned Ornament, Red White Green Stripe:  2 in. W x 6 in. H
